Business Brief -- Midlantic Corp.:
   Pacts to Sell Four Banks
   Reached With 2 Companies
The other two, Merchants National Bank  Trust Co. of
Syracuse and Union National Bank in Albany, will be acquired
by Onbancorp., which is based in Syracuse, N.Y., for $89.9
million.
   The four banks have total assets of $2.49 billion.
Midlantic had assets of $18.2 billion as of last Dec. 31.